1-hr AQI

Last updated Jan 18, 2017 18:47 CDT


The 1-hr AQI is the value that would result from a monitor’s current concentration persisting for the entire AQI averaging period. The map above includes the pollutants Ozone, PM-2.5, and PM-10.
